[03:28] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the church choir singing with the timpani accents between phrases, I also say with tubular bell accents, a low string bass and cello drone underneath throughout and harp arpeggios. &gt;&gt; [singing]'

[03:40] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: '[music] &gt;&gt; You probably noticed that all the prompting is taking place in one window rather than having a lyrics window and a style window or anything like that. It\'s'

[03:52] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'all here, so you just tell it exactly what you want. You tell it the style right up front with all of those details and then if you\'ve got your own custom lyrics, you simply give it the lyrics header. You can use all the voice, chorus, bridge tags that you\'re used to. One thing it does not do very well from'

[04:05] [scene:talk]
