AUDIO: 'and the lip sync. Every time you do a generation here in the OpenArt platform, you have the ability to add lip sync to the video. Once you\'ve got the audio the way you like it, you click lip sync video and then you\'re brought to that interface and you can choose whichever lip sync model you\'d like to go along'

[04:52] [scene:talk]
