AUDIO: 'And the way it handles it is it breaks the song up into three different sections, each one describing an image. Now we won\'t listen to the whole song, but I just want you to hear how it did it. So let\'s just pop in here where the lyrics start and you can see what I\'m talking about. &gt;&gt; [music]'

