[10:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'model, super fast generations, high-quality music, adherence to the prompt, the ability to use timestamps, and the ability to influence [music] the outcome with the images. It\'s all worked very well. But, there\'s a couple of things that\'s lacking. It\'s consistency'

